			<abstract>
				<p>Testimony of Ota Klinger, which became a part of the “documentation campaign” in Prague. Klinger describes the death of his fellow
					prisoner Jan Herrmann during an Allied air raid on the Schwarzheide labor camp.</p>
			</abstract>


